00:55:04.066 --> 00:55:05.726 A:middle
Now, to close out materials, we

00:55:05.726 --> 00:55:06.316 A:middle
have two more material

00:55:06.316 --> 00:55:07.356 A:middle
properties that I want to

00:55:07.356 --> 00:55:09.256 A:middle
